episodes.title: Surviving A Cult And Childhood Trauma
episodes.description:
Cult survivor of Curly Thornton Ministries speaks up on the teachings and abuse that traumatized her as a child. Catie Reay turned to alcohol and drugs at a very young age to cope with daily life. Listen in to find out what she is doing about it now.

Welcome to the Soberoso Podcast where we invite guests and listeners from around the world to join us in "Sharing Our Passion For Recovery".
